226
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:07,506
You don’t have to force yourself.
If you don’t want to...

227
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:08,550
I’ll do it.

228
00:21:08,550 --> 00:21:08,553
I’ll do it.
But Shion was different.

229
00:21:08,553 --> 00:21:11,746
But Shion was different.

230
