- You think so?

241
00:22:48,093 --> 00:22:49,893
After finding a dream,

242
00:22:50,860 --> 00:22:52,553
little by little,

243
00:22:53,066 --> 00:22:55,913
I finally became able to talk about

244
00:22:57,359 --> 00:22:59,713
the bullying I endured.

245
00:23:01,363 --> 00:23:04,120
Interaction was terrifying,

246
00:23:05,530 --> 00:23:09,206
and the memories were painful,

247
00:23:10,540 --> 00:23:13,033
but step by step, I moved forward.

248
00:23:14,866 --> 00:23:17,660
That is how we've survived.

249
00:23:19,733 --> 00:23:22,220
That’s amazing.

250
00:23:22,384 --> 00:23:25,120
You really made your dream come true.

251
00:23:25,120 --> 00:23:30,013
For me, the piano is proof
that I've truly lived.

252
00:23:30,446 --> 00:23:31,166
What?

253
00:23:32,153 --> 00:23:33,340
Thanks to you two.

254
00:23:35,293 --> 00:23:39,906
Knowing you were staying strong somewhere
taught me that I couldn't give up.

255
00:23:41,653 --> 00:23:43,806
That’s why I was able to
keep playing.

256
00:23:47,746 --> 00:23:49,220
It’s thanks to you two.

257
00:23:53,031 --> 00:23:54,240
It's here.

258
00:23:55,980 --> 00:23:58,246
This is how it turned out.

259
00:24:01,873 --> 00:24:03,346
